    "long_instructions": "## AI as a Hospital Triage Nurse\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to choose which two patients to assist first. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. **Add the PDF** with the six patient profiles into AI Chat. \r\n2. **Copy and paste** the following prompt into AI Chat. Press **Send** and read the response:\r\n\r\n>You are a hospital triage nurse. Read these six patient profiles and choose which two I should help first. Explain why you selected these two patients.\r\n\r\n3. Find the section in your Activity Guide called \"AI’s Selections\" and answer the questions.\r\n4. Revise your prompt to AI Chat and have it prioritize the same things you did.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure how to revise your prompt?**]\r\nTry this:\r\n>Now make your selection by prioritizing younger patients and patients with high pain levels.\r\n:::\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n",
